515
00:35:56,784 --> 00:35:57,758
Scott: Yeah, it's, you know.

516
00:35:58,900 --> 00:36:08,460
Scott: But yeah, so, you know, a train is really just like, you know, it has a schedule, you can't necessarily always go when you want, but it's like, it'll get you there when you need, right?

517
00:36:08,720 --> 00:36:19,140
